{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1332057, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "沃顿那几个人也是gpa前一还是前几，就算今年申请也能申请到顶校\n", "timestamp": 1616682433, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332073, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "应该说清华的整体资源不行，不能把锅推给院长", "timestamp": 1616682550, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332080, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 确实，但gpa在申phd中不那么重要。他如果没有沃顿交换和推荐信，今年申请也申请不到顶校。", "timestamp": 1616682598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332081, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: gpa是不重要，但它可以量化的反映一个人的能力", "timestamp": 1616682630, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332085, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 大环境和个人经历造成的吧，毕竟海外商科phd基本是经管两百号人中的个位数。", "timestamp": 1616682646, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332086, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你没有高gpa你觉得老师能放你去沃顿或者伯克利交换？", "timestamp": 1616682658, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332087, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 是个门槛", "timestamp": 1616682677, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332091, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "歪楼，那么贵系直博商科有希望吗", "timestamp": 1616682698, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1332098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 261960, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 有啊 今